      "parameters": {
        "width": 563,
        "height": 678,
        "content": "## 🎬 AI Location Scout Assistant\nThis workflow acts as your personal film location scout. It searches for locations via Google Maps, analyzes them using AI for cinematic potential, saves details to Google Sheets, and notifies you on Slack.\n\n### How it works\n1. **Chat Input:** Enter a keyword (e.g., \"Cyberpunk streets in Tokyo\").\n2. **Search:** Queries Google Places API.\n3. **AI Analysis:** An AI agent writes a \"Director's Commentary\" for each spot.\n4. **Save & Notify:** Saves to Sheets and alerts Slack.\n\n### Setup steps\n1. **Google Cloud:** Enable \"Places API (New)\" and get an API Key.\n2. **Google Sheets:** Create a sheet with headers: `場所名`, `住所`, `評価(星)`, `AI監督のコメント`, `GoogleMapリンク`.\n3. **Config Node:** Update the `Workflow Configuration` node with your API Key, Sheet ID, and Slack Channel ID."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
